author: sussman
msg: Bikeshed experimentation:  if a file or dir has regular, userland
properties... but those props aren't (C)onflicted or (M)odified
locally, let's at least show an underscore in the 2nd column of status
(generate_status_codes):  take a prop-time arg;  show underscore if
this arg is non-zero, but not C or M.
